"{\"uid\": \"travelweekly.com.au-demonstrations-in-paris-follow-preliminary-election-results-ahead-of-2024-olympic-paralympic-games\", \"entities\": [{\"sentence\": \"Store windows have become the target of demonstrators in Paris this week as tensions rise in the French capital after the right-wing National Rally (NR) party took the lead in preliminary election results.\", \"from\": 0, \"to\": 205, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 57, \"end\": 62, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 0.999999936028191, \"rank\": 6.397172572706784e-08, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}, {\"begin\": 97, \"end\": 103, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/French_language\", \"score\": 0.6022466298927962, \"rank\": 0.5278207455193734, \"text\": \"French\", \"types\": [\"Q315\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/French_language\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/French_language\"}, {\"begin\": 133, \"end\": 147, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/National_Rally\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"National Rally\", \"types\": [\"Q7278\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/National_Rally\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/National_Rally\"}, {\"begin\": 149, \"end\": 151, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Network_Rail\", \"score\": 0.9999999999440661, \"rank\": 5.529078489879059e-11, \"text\": \"NR\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Network_Rail\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Network_Rail\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The news comes less than four weeks away from the first events of the 2024 Olympic and Paralympic Games which will be held across the city.\", \"from\": 207, \"to\": 346, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 294, \"end\": 310, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paralympic_Games\", \"score\": 0.998511571451826, \"rank\": 0.001142846690837337, \"text\": \"Paralympic Games\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paralympic_Games\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paralympic_Games\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"TheNew York Postreported the streets of Paris to be akin to a warzone this week after thousands of left-wing protestors stood in fiery opposition to the NR.\", \"from\": 348, \"to\": 504, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 388, \"end\": 393, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 0.999999936028191, \"rank\": 6.397172572706784e-08, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}, {\"begin\": 501, \"end\": 503, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Network_Rail\", \"score\": 0.9999999999440661, \"rank\": 5.529078489879059e-11, \"text\": \"NR\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Network_Rail\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Network_Rail\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Marine Le Pen who fronts the NR took 33 per cent total of votes in the decisive first round of France's legislative elections.\", \"from\": 506, \"to\": 632, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 506, \"end\": 519, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Marine_Le_Pen\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Marine Le Pen\", \"types\": [\"Q82955\", \"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Marine_Le_Pen\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Marine_Le_Pen\"}, {\"begin\": 535, \"end\": 537, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Network_Rail\", \"score\": 0.9999999999440661, \"rank\": 5.529078489879059e-11, \"text\": \"NR\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Network_Rail\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Network_Rail\"}, {\"begin\": 601, \"end\": 607, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/French_Third_Republic\", \"score\": 0.9530005532927744, \"rank\": 0.04707394248612387, \"text\": \"France\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/French_Third_Republic\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/French_Third_Republic\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"A united bloc of left-leaning parties operating as the New Popular Front pulled 28 per cent of votes while incumbent President Macron's centrist party only saw 20 per cent of the nations support.\", \"from\": 634, \"to\": 829, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 693, \"end\": 706, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Popular_front\", \"score\": 0.9999974027066024, \"rank\": 2.597300209088989e-06, \"text\": \"Popular Front\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Popular_front\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Popular_front\"}, {\"begin\": 751, \"end\": 767, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Emmanuel_Macron\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"President Macron\", \"types\": [\"Q82955\", \"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Emmanuel_Macron\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Emmanuel_Macron\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Footage posted online shows protestors launching projectiles and fireworks at police and smashing shop front windows in a sight that has become synonymous with Parisian protests.\", \"from\": 831, \"to\": 1009, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"As of 4 July, Smartraveller has France marked as a yellow degree of danger and has not told Australian travellers to reconsider plans to travel.\", \"from\": 1011, \"to\": 1155, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1043, \"end\": 1049, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/French_Third_Republic\", \"score\": 0.9530005532927744, \"rank\": 0.04707394248612387, \"text\": \"France\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/French_Third_Republic\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/French_Third_Republic\"}, {\"begin\": 1103, \"end\": 1113, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Australian_Government\", \"score\": 0.9963206647293863, \"rank\": 0.002369085038105689, \"text\": \"Australian\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Australian_Government\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Australian_Government\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"France will hold national elections on 30 June and 7 July,\\\" Smarttraveller reads.\", \"from\": 1157, \"to\": 1239, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1158, \"end\": 1164, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/French_Third_Republic\", \"score\": 0.9530005532927744, \"rank\": 0.04707394248612387, \"text\": \"France\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/French_Third_Republic\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/French_Third_Republic\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"Demonstrations may occur around these dates, which could cause disruptions to transport and other public services.\", \"from\": 1241, \"to\": 1356, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Avoid protests and demonstrations and follow the advice of local authorities (see 'Safety').\", \"from\": 1357, \"to\": 1449, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"France will host the Olympic and Paralympic Games between 26 July - 8 September.\", \"from\": 1451, \"to\": 1532, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1452, \"end\": 1458, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/French_Third_Republic\", \"score\": 0.9530005532927744, \"rank\": 0.04707394248612387, \"text\": \"France\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/French_Third_Republic\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/French_Third_Republic\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Travel delays are likely during this period.\\\"\", \"from\": 1533, \"to\": 1578, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Smartraveller also reminds travellers that France's national terrorist alert remains at the highest level.\", \"from\": 1580, \"to\": 1686, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1623, \"end\": 1629, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/French_Third_Republic\", \"score\": 0.9530005532927744, \"rank\": 0.04707394248612387, \"text\": \"France\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/French_Third_Republic\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/French_Third_Republic\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"Expect high-level security measures nationwide, especially in venue cities, including schools, places of worship, shopping centres, and landmarks.\\\"\", \"from\": 1688, \"to\": 1836, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"If you are travelling to Paris or France, we recommend checking back in on SmartTraveller warnings prior to departure.\", \"from\": 1838, \"to\": 1956, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1863, \"end\": 1868, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 0.999999936028191, \"rank\": 6.397172572706784e-08, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}, {\"begin\": 1872, \"end\": 1878, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/French_Third_Republic\", \"score\": 0.9530005532927744, \"rank\": 0.04707394248612387, \"text\": \"France\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/French_Third_Republic\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/French_Third_Republic\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Feature image: Riot police in Paris.\", \"from\": 1958, \"to\": 1994, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1973, \"end\": 1984, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Riot_police\", \"score\": 0.999999722951354, \"rank\": 2.7704861591836563e-07, \"text\": \"Riot police\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Riot_police\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Riot_police\"}, {\"begin\": 1988, \"end\": 1993, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 0.999999936028191, \"rank\": 6.397172572706784e-08, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Source: The Su